snippet.title: Hollywood Star Johnny Depp Insists He’s ‘No Wife Beater’
snippet.description:
Court case concludes with the actor's legal team labelling Amber Heard a 'compulsive liar' Johnny Depp is “no wife beater” and his reputation was besmirched by an article in The Sun in which the newspaper acted as “both judge and jury” about his character, the actor's lawyer said on Tuesday.
